                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "客户姓名：王先生\n性别/年龄：男 / 48岁\n职业：企业管理层（IT公司CEO）\n消费等级：高端客户（VIP）",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "JRprh",
                          "name": "docSep2",
                          "fill": "#D6DEE8",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Q75UQ",
                          "name": "secTitle2",
                          "fill": "#0F172A",
                          "content": "第二部分：客户健康信息分析",
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "sxgh6",
                          "name": "secContent2",
                          "fill": "#1F2937",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "体检时间：2026年2月20日\n\n异常指标总结：\n• 低密度脂蛋白胆固醇(LDL-C)：4.34（中度升高）\n• 同型半胱氨酸(Hcy)：18.5（严重升高）\n• 血红蛋白(HGB)：175（轻度升高）\n\n心脑血管风险等级：高风险\n未来5年心梗/脑卒中风险：约 12-15%",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "vAoYc",
                          "name": "docSep3",
                          "fill": "#D6DEE8",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "UyihJ",
                          "name": "secTitle4",
                          "fill": "#0F172A",
                          "content": "第三部分：真人成功案例",
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "llgi1",
                          "name": "secContent4",
                          "fill": "#1F2937",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "案例一：赵先生（52岁） - 血脂异常改善\n• 干预前：LDL-C 5.1 mmol/L，伴有轻微头晕\n• 干预后：LDL-C 降至 2.8 mmol/L，头晕消失，精力明显提升\n\n案例二：孙女士（45岁） - 同型半胱氨酸显著下降\n• 干预前：Hcy 22.5 μmol/L，家族性高血压风险\n• 干预后：Hcy 降至 11.2 μmol/L，血压趋于平稳，整体代谢改善",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "3T2Nl",
                          "name": "docSep5",
                          "fill": "#D6DEE8",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Vp26N",
                          "name": "secTitle5",
                          "fill": "#0F172A",
                          "content": "第四部分：投资回报分析 (ROI)",
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Bhw6N",
                          "name": "secContent5",
                          "fill": "#1F2937",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "• 不干预的隐形成本：预计未来3-5年医疗支出约 40-60万元\n• 本方案年度总投资：156,200元\n• 预期收益：降低重大心脑血管疾病发生风险 70%以上，生活质量显著提升\n• 综合投资回报率 (ROI)：约 150% - 200%",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "UALCi",
                          "name": "docSep6",
                          "fill": "#D6DEE8",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "dUHoe",
                          "name": "secTitle6",
                          "fill": "#0F172A",
                          "content": "第五部分：转化强化与承诺保障",
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "fddTL",
                          "name": "secContent6",
                          "fill": "#1F2937",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "• 指标改善承诺：若按方案执行未达预期目标指标，提供免费强化疗程\n• 症状缓解承诺：针对头晕、乏力等核心不适，预期 1-3个月内明显缓解\n• 服务品质承诺：全程私人医生级管理服务，24小时健康咨询响应",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "rectangle",
                          "id": "ig7sA",
                          "name": "docSep7",
                          "fill": "#D6DEE8",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": 1
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "NCgOx",
                          "name": "secTitle7",
                          "fill": "#0F172A",
                          "content": "第六部分：行动号召与购买建议",
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 16,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "VPRj7",
                          "name": "secContent7",
                          "fill": "#1F2937",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "方案 A（推荐）：极致保障金 158,200元 / 12个月\n方案 B：强化改善期 76,000元 / 3个月\n方案 C：基础预防期 45,600元 / 1个月\n\n【完整方案建议】\n优选一（储值方案）：100万海心卡\n• 涵盖项目：心脑血管预防套餐 + 同型半胱氨酸靶向调理（项目金划扣）\n• 优势：最高性价比，享受项目金 1.2倍 增效，方案灵活性最高",
                          "lineHeight": 1.85,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
